'''''Memoria descriptiva sobre Tucumán''''' ({{lang-es|Descriptive memoir of Tucumán}}) is an Argentine 1834 book of [[Juan Bautista Alberdi]]. It was a work requested by [[Alejandro Heredia]], governor of the [[Tucumán Province]].

